- Database Setup
////

- Central Server
initialized with
[
    npm init -y
    npm install express axios cors dotenv
    npm install --save-dev nodemon
]

- Mongo Server
[
    npm init -y
    npm install express mongoose cors dotenv
    npm install --save-dev nodemon    
]

- Postgres Server
created trough intellij
Spring Boot with imports [Spring WEB, Spring Data JPA, PostgeSQL Data]
